de.oaam.model.oaam.hardware

Interface HardwareContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Hardware, Subhardware
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HardwareContainerAImpl, HardwareImpl, SubhardwareImpl

    public interface HardwareContainerA
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. The root container of the hardware model

    The following features are supported:

    • Devices
    • Device Symmetries
    • Connections
    • Subhardware
    See Also:
    HardwarePackage.getHardwareContainerA()
